About This Company
The United Arab Emirates University is a federal institution located in the garden city of Al Ain, (population 380,000) in the United Arab Emirates.
The United Arab Emirates University serves 16,000 students in Colleges of Medicine and Health Sciences, Engineering, Science, Information Technology, Business and Economics, Food Systems, Education, Humanities and Social Sciences, and Shari'ah and Law.
